Acceptance

In order to receive this license, you must agree to its rules. The rules of this license are both obligations under your agreement and conditions to your license. You must not do anything with the software that triggers a rule that you cannot or will not follow.

Noncommercial Purposes Only

You may use the software for noncommercial purposes only. Noncommercial purposes are uses that are not intended for or directed toward commercial advantage or monetary compensation.

Personal, research, experimental, and hobby use are all allowed.  
Selling, licensing, or using the software in a product or service intended to make money is not allowed.

Redistribution

You may redistribute the software, including in source or object form, so long as you do not charge for it, or use it in a paid or commercial product or service.

No Trademark License

This license does not grant you any right in the trademarks, service marks, brand names, or logos of the licensor.

No Liability

As far as the law allows, the software comes as is, without any warranty or condition, and the licensor will not be liable to you for any damages arising out of the license or use of the software under this license.

Termination

If you use the software for commercial purposes, or otherwise break the rules of this license, your rights under it end automatically.

